A = data('if_octets.tx', filter=filter('plugin', 'interface', 'net-io') and filter('plugin_instance', 'e*') and (not filter('agent', '*'))).sum().scale(8).publish(label='A', enable=False)

C = (A).count().below(0, inclusive=True).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B*(C+1)).publish(label='D')

J = (H).count().below(0, inclusive=True).publish(label='J', enable=False)
K = (H*(L+1)).publish(label='K')
L = (I).count().below(0, inclusive=True).publish(label='L', enable=False)

M = (C*(K+1)).sum().publish(label='M')
N = (C+J).sum().publish(label='N')
